    "Wagering Tax"
  ],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Authorizes limited casino gaming in a single location in the City and County of Honolulu.  Establishes the Hawaii Gaming Control Commission.  Imposes a wagering tax on the monthly gross receipts received from casino gaming.  Establishes the State Gaming Fund.  Requires the Hawaii Gaming Commission to create and implement a Compulsive Gamblers Program.  Exempts the construction of any casino facility from county special assessments and certain special improvement district requirements.  Establishes certain civil service exemptions.  Appropriates funds with certain conditions."
    }
  ],
